\"MJXc-Node-68323\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-68324\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-68325\" class=\"mjx-mfrac\"><span class=\"mjx-box MJXc-stacked\" style=\"width: 0.495em; padding: 0px 0.12em;\"><span class=\"mjx-numerator\" style=\"font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.7em; top: -1.306em;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-68326\" class=\"mjx-mn\" style=\"\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">1</span></span></span><span class=\"mjx-denominator\" style=\"font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.7em; bottom: -0.621em;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-68327\" class=\"mjx-mn\" style=\"\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">6</span></span></span><span class=\"mjx-line\" style=\"border-bottom: 1.3px solid; top: -0.284em; width: 0.495em;\"></span></span><span class=\"mjx-vsize\" style=\"height: 1.362em; vertical-align: -0.439em;\"></span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-13615\">\\frac{1}{6}</script></span>, to find the mean, apply the formula: \n<div class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span class=\"mjx-chtml MJXc-display\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Element-13616-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"font-size: 114%; text-align: center; position: relative;\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot; display=&quot;block&quot;><msub><mi>&amp;#x03BC;</mi><mi>x</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-68328\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-68329\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-N